,{"pid":"f796ab8c485000396d9ee975effec56dff4dc2e5","tid":778871,"uid":61643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"唔好係唔係都要搵位入泛民得唔得呀？<br />\n玩JR真係要搵無資產嘅人先玩得起<br />\n唔係嘅話，幾千萬都幾下就無晒<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係有跟開郭卓堅啲JR，你就會發現只要法庭一受理，郭就會委託番李柱銘佢地做代表律師，咁泛民先可以上枱出聲<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係隨時法援都申請唔到.."},{"pid":"95af556a4a54fd42e79e7ed1d1e6fd150675a518","tid":778871,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2e3259510400bfc9152c20a4d778d11641a7f3e","tid":778871,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:09:40.000Z","msg":"問題又黎啦，某黨有成半人有法律背景，大把律師，另外一個黨直情係律師黨，成個黨都律師，<span style=\"color: red;\">點解次次要市民自發覆核仲要冇人幫?<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:26:37.000Z","msg":"冇比中國DQ嘅人=冇威脅/中國自己友"},{"pid":"4e927867eed0e5436afc5baba27ea71c5a5462b0","tid":778871,"uid":66686,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de59c06020b15570e094dada4d46143970860ab9","tid":778871,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f96341fa37eb23c4cd7362821667773e87acc06b","tid":778871,"uid":24824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:31:22.000Z","msg":"你已經犠牲好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:32:12.000Z","msg":"郭卓堅係BC黎, 仲有心過香港本土人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:31:00.000Z","msg":"BC輸左有得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得BNO輸左俾港共SM一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8bb8a35d9070c96988add6567e0e53d725ed3f","tid":778871,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T11:40:12.000Z","msg":"點樣可以捐錢俾佢？<im